Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭不要在這裡弄垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-讓我看下這個  -什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-看有沒有中獎\N別人扔的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 我還沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊滾蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:01:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生會發生什麼不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到自己會成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我住在這棟樓的\N最高層
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了和擁有100億的我結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10名美少女用身體勾引我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類史上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最完美的聚會\N現在確是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的最高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的最高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(佐佐木 秋)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(水戶 金)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:02:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-想要錢吧\N-再插深點小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(白木 優子)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(一色 桃子)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(遙 彩)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(遙 彩)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(澤村 玲子)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(吉瀨 菜菜子)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(三浦 惠理子)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再深點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出來了 出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(風間 由美)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(友田 真希)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的錢都用來賭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺目空一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下100億債務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處吃剩菜剩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年就成為這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(尋找想賺錢的男性)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助女性的工作\N不可能是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣想\N但是我沒有什麼可失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登陸需要面試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(背負100億負債的悲劇的我)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 是中田君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是我的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的中年面試官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是之前店子裡的秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很消極呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒變呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比之前還要漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我現在的老公相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它人也結婚了\N幸福得生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像不怎麼樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活該
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在恨我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多的錢誰都想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秋做的吧那事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想來應聘這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 怎麼可能泥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失禮不是欺詐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是已經登陸的人員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會員名單
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錢想養男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟老公男朋友以外的\N男人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種婦女多得很
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是跟這種婦女\N提供服務的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我有幾個公司\N但這公司最成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-公司  -是的股份公司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,股東都是你知道的\N那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們稱這些男人為狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:07:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為狗之前要通過\N所有股東的面試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是禮金100萬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我們為了錢脫衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次你為了錢出賣肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 你能得到錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有拒絕的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過了面試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了錢 你就答應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來教你該怎麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前 先去洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 采你現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你們倆個在一起\N太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來調教一下狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 是一條好狗呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愣著幹什廖 趴著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我當會員打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是中田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗是沒有名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是主人的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是主人的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我侍奉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我侍奉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我侍奉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始做什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把腳弄乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-主人這樣可以嗎\N-更有禮貌一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這棣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要偷懶 好好做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到牙齒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 吃腳的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呀 乳頭都硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要控制吧 你這麼敏感\N想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再爽點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一隻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:15:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的樣子太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-已經開始了嗎\N-你們太慢了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟我們打招呼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-應該叫主人吧\N-是的 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不要搞錯了 現在是調教\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有恨你 反而很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到這麼好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調教的有點過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是有一點呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好調教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是你侍奉她們兩位\N-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不要有感覺 -好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-讓她們爽吧 -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-起來  -好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是主人的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來侍奉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是主人的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來侍奉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來侍奉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把舌頭伸進腳趾中間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己舔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更嚴厲的調教一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把舌頭伸出來 好好的舔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-太棒了  -近一點
