Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.43,0:44:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呀 現在變得會說了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.74,0:44:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那來插了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.76,0:45:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.27,0:45:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎麼樣 爽吧  -爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.97,0:45:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不能只有自己爽\N-明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.08,0:45:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好好侍奉吧  -好好插
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.68,0:45:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-就這樣 手不是這樣放的吧\N-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.09,0:45:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你爽不爽無所謂\N-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.99,0:45:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-只要肉棒硬著就行\N-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.20,0:45:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-讓她好好爽爽  -好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.21,0:45:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-爽嗎爽嗎  -爽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.91,0:45:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我也很爽 好硬呀\N-是呀 好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.62,0:46:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬 好爽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.22,0:46:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓肉棒再硬些 再硬些
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.43,0:46:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽死了 好硬
