Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.44,0:46:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好好加油  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.04,0:46:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.05,0:46:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-經不起表揚的\N-真的嗎 不能射了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.75,0:46:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.96,0:46:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能休息 讓肉棒好好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.56,0:46:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽呀
