Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.38,0:47:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-工作有進步剛才很危險吧\N-謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.89,0:47:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再來工作  -好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.81,0:47:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力 用力插
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.02,0:47:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的小穴很爽吧
