Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.10,0:48:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄髒了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.51,0:48:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 就是條狗
