Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.01,0:48:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-說了不能射的\-對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.22,0:48:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.02,0:48:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.53,0:48:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-都是小便呀\N-都是尿我也想了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.43,0:49:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在這裡來吧\N-是呀 在這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.05,0:49:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了呀 都喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.16,0:49:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.67,0:49:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都喝了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.07,0:49:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好喝嗎  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.97,0:49:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你的獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.98,0:49:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有獎勵不錯吧  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.88,0:49:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可以讓他合格吧  -是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.49,0:49:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.99,0:49:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-還不能讓你接客戶  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.70,0:49:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.10,0:50:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少分
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.70,0:50:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,態度還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.41,0:50:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒還不錯
