Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.23,0:52:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的狗要服務很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.04,0:52:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡太弱了 就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.04,0:52:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 所以要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.15,0:52:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來調教你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.56,0:52:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來調教你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.17,0:52:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼大了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.47,0:52:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼硬了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.18,0:52:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真的不錯呀
