Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.93,0:53:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄出來
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.93,0:53:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到肉棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.63,0:53:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是的 是這個肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.84,0:53:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你好好爽爽
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.15,0:54:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睾丸
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.37,0:54:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你按摩罩九
