Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.09,0:54:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.29,0:54:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-形狀好像在變化\N-真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.60,0:54:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看比剛才硬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.41,0:55:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很硬吧 看看怎麼樣
