Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.83,0:55:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉圈轉圈呀
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.24,0:55:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常熱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.95,0:55:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在變硬大呀 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.56,0:55:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想多摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.86,0:55:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是罩九
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.77,0:55:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要摸 很興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.47,0:56:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊弄罩丸\N一邊看哪裡敏感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.88,0:56:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.69,0:56:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體在抖呀
