Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.71,0:56:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.61,0:56:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣這個
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.02,0:56:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這樣很爽吧\N-已經出水了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.92,0:56:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.13,0:57:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-出水了 真的  -真的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.84,0:57:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.15,0:57:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡這樣弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.76,0:57:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好滑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.36,0:57:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒說很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.78,0:57:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.28,0:57:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.29,0:57:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來看來看
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.99,0:58:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.90,0:58:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.81,0:58:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個很爽 越來越硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.41,0:58:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好爽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.92,0:58:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加爽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.02,0:58:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄快點了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.23,0:58:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經受不了了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.83,0:58:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.13,0:58:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.95,0:58:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
