Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.16,0:59:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.46,0:59:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓你好好練習練習
